{"tid":367094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寓言故事分享","createTime":"2017-08-20T13:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T13:38:01.000Z","uid":137811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be1beee5ba46ea79269c4347b51baf83c9bfb10a","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"個故事係我聽返嚟嘅，我唔知出處同唔清楚內容，各位巴絲明就算啦~<br />\n<br />\n從前，有條廢青得閑到去揾螞蟻吹水，佢問啲蟻：「喂，點解你地有口都講唔到野嘅？亅啲蟻就答話：「我點知喎，出世就係咁。亅堆蟻入面有個啊伯，同佢地講：<br />\n「唉，少年，是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好耐好耐以前，螞蟻族入面有個暴君，駁佢嘴---殺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔贊成佢---殺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢覺得你唔妥佢---都殺！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有一堆反對佢嘅螞蟻成日係到嘈，要求罷免呢個王，但係其他蟻就唔係咁諗啦，「屌你地，阻撚住揾食，我仲有頭家要養，我要返工，不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亅<br />\n<br />\n結果最後，反對派因為只有少數人支持而全減，剩落嚟嘅，只有個啲冇參與冇出餐嘅蟻。暴君死咗，但係佢幾個後代都係咁，人人都唔敢出聲，久而久之，螞蟻一族就連開口講野都唔得啦。亅<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2a052977f74b997c25476d4488d0a9f35c459b","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"10e6112a304f15ecc6ebd185a2805d107571eedb","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96f0288e5882622e2ce2fb3bffe4d978aa375e1","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:28:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4ec0adf529e30716018c4b48c179dddd26eecc61","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9d5cad161097cf1a3d0d40ec71fa3f07adaf2ad5","tid":367094,"uid":137811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e9c92c5fddaddd6ca28126358c1f2